La Cave Musik and Lugi Musik Worldwide have presented Nigerian artiste, Lugi, in a new music video for his song, ‘Where Your Oga Dey?’. Produced by Brace, Where Your Oga Dey is a true encounter of the artiste and the police. It’s re-released in solidarity with the #EndSARSNow campaign. Clement Chuks Simon, LUGI is a graduate of Political Science from the University of Port Harcourt and holds a Master’s in Business Management from Plymouth University in the United Kingdom.